# Testing Standards

## Backend (pytest)
- Use FastAPI `TestClient` from `starlette.testclient`
- Test HTTP status codes and response body shape
- One test file per router or feature area under `backend/tests/`

## Frontend (Vitest + React Testing Library)
- Smoke-test that components render and key interactions work
- Query by role/label, not implementation details (no test IDs unless necessary)
- Place tests beside components: `Component.test.tsx`

## Principles
- Test behavior and contracts, not internal implementation
- Each challenge requirement should map to at least one test when feasible
- Run before submit: `pytest` (from `backend/`), `npm test` (from `frontend/`)
